name: Space Clearing Candle/ Intention candle / organic
description:
Space clearing candle made with soy wax, essential oils, and topped with palo santo, frankincense, pink sea salt, and a quartz crystal. It cleanses negative energy, absorbs “bad vibes,” and resets the energy of a space.

*Essential oil candles are a muted scent. There is no synthetic fragrance oil in our candles.*

Organic, non-GMO, cruelty-free, and free from harmful chemicals. Labels are printed on recycled paper with soy-based inks.
